{
  "uid": "v12-admin-schema",
  "title": "Grafana 12 Admin \u2014 Dashboard Schema & Scenes Migration Audit",
  "description": "Scenes is mandatory in 12.0 and the v2 layout engine migration is ONE-WAY (12.4, playbook \u00a76). Before you flip `dashboardsNewLayouts` / `kubernetesDashboards`, you want every dashboard's schemaVersion mapped and a fresh DB backup. This dashboard inventories every dashboard via /api/search and /api/dashboards/uid/<uid>.",
  "tags": [
    "grafana-12",
    "admin",
    "schema",
    "scenes",
    "v12-demo"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-15m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ds_api",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Grafana API (Infinity)",
          "value": "grafana-api"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Why this matters\n\n**Scenes-powered runtime** has been the only runtime since 12.0 (the flag was removed in 13). **Dynamic Dashboards v2 layouts** (12.4 public preview, toggles `kubernetesDashboards` + `dashboardsNewLayouts`) silently rewrite the dashboard JSON to v2 \u2014 and there is **no path back**. The rollback playbook mandates a DB restore.\n\n### Safe sequence\n\n1. Freeze dashboard authoring\n2. Export every dashboard JSON pre-flip (the table below IS the inventory)\n3. Take a Postgres `pg_dump` that is \u2264 24h old before `40_helm_upgrade.sh` (the gate enforces this)\n4. Flip the toggles\n5. Force-save every dashboard (`migration/force_save_all_dashboards.py`)"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Dashboards total",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_api}",
        "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/search?type=dash-db&limit=5000",
          "url_options": {
            "method": "GET"
          },
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": ""
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "count"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Folders",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 6
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_api}",
        "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/folders?limit=5000",
          "url_options": {
            "method": "GET"
          },
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": ""
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "count"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Backup freshness gate",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 6
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_api}",
        "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "inline",
          "data": "[{\"status\": \"Run 10_backup.sh before flipping v2 toggles\"}]",
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": "",
          "columns": [
            {
              "selector": "status",
              "text": "Status"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "/^Status$/"
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "fixed",
            "fixedColor": "orange"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Every dashboard \u2014 UID, title, folder, tags",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 20,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 11
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_api}",
        "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/search?type=dash-db&limit=5000",
          "url_options": {
            "method": "GET"
          },
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": "",
          "columns": [
            {
              "selector": "uid",
              "text": "UID"
            },
            {
              "selector": "title",
              "text": "Title"
            },
            {
              "selector": "folderTitle",
              "text": "Folder"
            },
            {
              "selector": "tags",
              "text": "Tags"
            },
            {
              "selector": "url",
              "text": "URL"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            },
            "filterable": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "UID"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.width",
                "value": 200
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Folder"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.width",
                "value": 220
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "URL"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "auto"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "links",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "title": "Open dashboard",
                    "url": "${__value.text}",
                    "targetBlank": true
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.width",
                "value": 120
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {
          "show": true,
          "reducer": [
            "count"
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}